    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To solve this globally (on all projects), after pressing <strong>ctrl + shift + r</strong>, click on the top right corner of the window on the <strong>three dots button</strong>, then click on <em><strong>Select Working Set</strong></em>, <strong>tick</strong> both <em>Java Main Source</em> and <em>Java Test Source</em> and voila.</p>\n"
